	</p>
	<p lang="en-US" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<br/>
	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">
			<b>Short
Messaging Services</b>
		</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">The Short Messaging Service (</span>
		<span lang="en-US">
			<b>'SMS'</b>
		</span>
		<span lang="en-US">)
where provided to update the OVMC application. The time to deliver the SMS is dependent on several factors such as upon the traffic on
the mobile network and whether the visa applicant mobile phone is within reach and switched on and cannot therefore be guaranteed by
Oman Post. Oman Post is not a mobile network operator and does not guarantee the delivery of SMS text messages.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">The applicant confirms that they have provided an accurate mobile number for receiving SMS. The applicant confirms that
they are the owner or the legitimate user of the mobile device or phone. The applicant acknowledges that using another person's mobile
