	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">For operational reasons Oman Post may vary the technical specification of the optional SMS services without notice.
In the event of any change to the optional SMS services these terms and conditions are to be treated as varied accordingly.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">The applicant acknowledges that the optional SMS services may, at any time, be adversely affected by problems with the
