	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">The applicant is responsible for paying charges for the message origination. Charges once paid for this optional SMS service will not be refunded under any circumstances.</span>
