	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">Oman Post specifically excludes all liability of any kind (including negligence) in respect of any third party information or other material made available on, or which can be accessed using this optional SMS text services.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">These terms and conditions are governed by the law of the country of operation and both parties submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of the country of operation.</span>
	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">
			<b>Spam</b>
		</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">Oman Post does not tolerate spam. Oman Post website/s or communication tools shall not be used to send spam or otherwise send content that would violate the terms and conditions of Oman Post user agreement.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">it is not permitted to license, add, modify, deface, hack, misuse or abuse Oman Post’ website or the contents therein.</span>
	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">
			<b>Fraudulent Activities / Bogus Employment Offers</b>
		</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">It has come to Oman Post’ attention that,
individuals misrepresenting themselves as Oman Post’s agents or
representatives have approached people to offer fraudulent/fictitious
employment opportunities, with the intent to steal personal
information or solicit money from people. Oman Post encourage the
applicant to exercise caution and common sense when receiving any
such employment offer, which requires payment of any fees/money, or
promises a work visa in exchange for money. The said offers are
completely fake and not valid. Oman Post is not a recruitment agency
and does not offer recruitment services. Scammers operate primarily
via the internet, email, phone etc. Oman Post warns people to beware
of such scams.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">Please be advised that, Oman Post is a postal
company and works only with agents and diplomatic office for the
purpose of fulfilling administrative requirements of application
processing. Neither Oman Post nor its representatives will ask for
money from individuals under any circumstances to lure them with
employment opportunities either in Oman Post or outside. If you
receive any offer that purports to be from Oman Post, which ask for
money, these types of offers are fraudulent.</span>
	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">
			<b>Other Fraudulent Activities</b>
		</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">Please also be aware of individuals
misrepresenting themselves as Oman Post employees, who have been
known to approach customers entering some of the buildings where our
offices are located, and have tried to extract payment from these
customers before allowing them to proceed to our offices.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">On no occasion will customers be asked for a cash
payment to be made at the point of entry to any of the buildings
where our offices are located. Appointments and services are either
paid for in advance online.</span>
	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">If you are aware of any such incidents, please report them to ASYAD’s Compliance Officer (</span>
		<font color="#467886">
			<u>
				<a href="mailto:compliance@asyad.com">
					<span lang="en-US">compliance@asyad.com</span>
				</a>
			</u>
		</font>
		<span lang="en-US">
) as soon as possible.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">Oman Post takes these matters extremely seriously and will notify local law enforcement to investigate and prosecute any illegal activities we are made aware of.</span>
	</p>
	<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">Under no circumstances will Oman Post be liable or responsible for any loss, damages, expenses or inconvenience resulting from these unauthorized persons and/or activities.</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
		<span lang="en-US">
			<b>Consequential Loss. </b>
		</span>
	</p>
	<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-left: 0.5in; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
Oman Post shall not be liable for any loss of business, interruption
of business, lost profits or goodwill, or other indirect, special,
incidental, exemplary or consequential damages of any kind (in each
case whether direct or indirect) arising out of OVMC, even if they
have been advised of the possibility of such damages and whether they
had any knowledge that such damage might be incurred, and
notwithstanding any failure of essential purpose of any limited
remedy.</p>
