					</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
			</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
					<span lang="en-US">
						<b>Data collected through analytics tags&nbsp;</b>
					</span>
					<span lang="en-US">such as the effectiveness of functionalities, features and user preferences relating to our digital services.</span>
				</p>
			</li>
		</ol>
		</div>
		<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Note:&nbsp;</b>
			</span>
			<span lang="en-US">Where
you disclose Personal Data of another individual to us, you undertake
to ensure that the individual whose Personal Data is supplied to us
has, where required under applicable data protection laws, authorised
the disclosure, is informed of, understands and acknowledges the
provisions of this Privacy Statement.</span>
		</p>
		<p lang="en-US" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<br/>
			<br/>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Use
of Personal Data</b>
			</span>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">Specifically,
we use data for </span>
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Provision of
registration services.</b>
			</span>
			<span lang="en-US"> This includes,
but not limited to, administering application for work visa.</span>
		</p>
		<p lang="en-US" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<br/>
			<br/>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Disclosure
or Sharing of Personal Data</b>
			</span>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">We
share Personal Data with third parties for purposes justified by
legal bases and strictly on a need-to-know basis. Oman Post will
never sell your personal data.</span>
		</p>
		<p lang="en-US" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<br/>
			<br/>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Retention
of Personal Data</b>
