		</ol>
		</div>
		<p lang="en-US" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<br/>
			<br/>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Access and Correction</b>
			</span>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">If you would like to request for access to your Personal Data which you have earlier provided to Oman Post or information about the ways in
which the Personal Data you have provided has been used or disclosed by Oman Post, please contact us to our registered address in Oman.</span>
		</p>
		<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">Oman Post may charge an access fee to cover the reasonable cost of retrieving the information and supplying it to you. </span>
		</p>
		<p lang="en-US" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<br/>
			<br/>
		</p>
		<p style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">
				<b>Updates to this Privacy Statement</b>
			</span>
		</p>
		<p align="justify" style="line-height: 108%; margin-bottom: 0.11in">
			<span lang="en-US">We may amend this Privacy Statement from time to time. 
				The current version of the Privacy Statement will be accessible on our website.
				Please review this Privacy Statement when you use our website.</span>
		</p>
	</div>

	</DialogContent>
